room_title: Escape room "The Creighton House Attic" by Amelia Island Escape Rooms in Jacksonville
room_description:
Your crew climbs upstairs, boards creaking the entire way to the top. As you open the door, you see nothing; it’s nearly pitch black inside. Still, you feel compelled to go in. Tentatively, you step into the room and the door suddenly slams shut! Voices echo around you, “One hour! Just one hour to escape… or stay forever.”
Can you learn the history of the mystical manor and find a way to escape the attic before you become a permanent resident?
